# The Malebranche — an artfully crafted intellect

![essence of The Malebranche](the-malebranche.png)
<!-- carbon badge (8-bit portrait): the-malebranche.tiff -->

**what —** The barb-forked guards of the barrators in their boiling pitch.

**why —** To torment the grafters — and to lie even to the travelers passing through.

**how —** With hooks, mockery, and a treachery that nearly traps the poets themselves.

**where —** Circle VIII — Fraud (barratry).

